Install a standard Linux machine with Apache

Configure an HTTPS server to work with Shibboleth.  

	/secure is protected by Shibboleth
	/unsecured is not

yum install these packages:
	  freetds
		client and libraries
	* freetds-devel
		developer tools

	  mysql
		client and libraries
	  mysql-libs
		(may be implied)
	  mysql-devel
		(probably not if MySQL-python works)
	* MySQL-python
		python driver for mysql

	* sqlite
		sqlite library and client

	  postgresql
		client programs an library
	* python-psycopg2
		python client

easy_install pip

pip install pymssql

pip install ipaddr

